      public Camp(String name, LocalDate startDate, LocalDate endDate, LocalDate closingDate, UserGroup userGroup, String location, int totalSlots, String description, Staff staffInCharge, boolean isVisible)

      Parameters:
      name - The name of the camp.
      startDate - The start date of the camp.
      endDate - The end date of the camp.
      closingDate - The closing date for camp registration.
      userGroup - The user group associated with the camp.
      location - The location of the camp.
      totalSlots - The total number of available slots in the camp.
      description - The description of the camp.
      staffInCharge - The staff member in charge of the camp.
      isVisible - Indicates whether the camp is visible.
